Class ObjectPair<T1,T2>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.minecraft.src.forge.ObjectPair<T1,T2>

    T1 - The type of the first value
    T2 - The Type of the second value

    public class ObjectPair<T1,T2>
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that holds two generic values, can be used as a Key/Value pair, but is used in forge as a frequency/object pair.
